hh3cPUMan.name: hh3cPUMan
hh3cPUMan.contactinfo: Platform Team Hangzhou H3C Tech. Co., Ltd. Hai-Dian District Beijing P.R. China http://www.h3c.com Zip:100085
hh3cPUMan.description: The PU includes those device like EC(Encoder), DC(Decoder) and ECR(Encoder Recorder). The PU will survey the remote video and audio. This MIB is defined to manage the PU as our private MIB node according to its specific capability.

hh3cPUisOnline.name: hh3cPUisOnline
hh3cPUisOnline.description: The PU online status indicates whether the PU is normally registered into the VM. True indicates that the PU is normally registered into the VM.

hh3cPUCMSAddr.name: hh3cPUCMSAddr
hh3cPUCMSAddr.description: The IP address of the CMS. All zero address indicates the CMS address is not configured.

hh3cPUVersionServerAddr.name: hh3cPUVersionServerAddr
hh3cPUVersionServerAddr.description: The IP address of the version server. All zero address indicates the version server is not configured or does not support remote upgrade.

hh3cPUExternalInputAlarmChannelID.name: hh3cPUExternalInputAlarmChannelID
hh3cPUExternalInputAlarmChannelID.description: The ID of the external input alarm channel.

hh3cPUExternalInputAlarmStatus.name: hh3cPUExternalInputAlarmStatus
hh3cPUExternalInputAlarmStatus.description: True indicates that the current channel has alarm.

hh3cPUExternalOutputAlarmChannelID.name: hh3cPUExternalOutputAlarmChannelID
hh3cPUExternalOutputAlarmChannelID.description: The ID of the external output alarm channel

hh3cPUExternalOutputAlarmStatus.name: hh3cPUExternalOutputAlarmStatus
hh3cPUExternalOutputAlarmStatus.description: True indicates that the current channel has alarm.

hh3cPUECCameraOnlines.name: hh3cPUECCameraOnlines
hh3cPUECCameraOnlines.description: Number of online cameras connected to an EC.

hh3cPUECCameraAvailRate.name: hh3cPUECCameraAvailRate
hh3cPUECCameraAvailRate.description: Camera available rate. That is, the ratio of available cameras to total cameras connected to an EC. It ranges from 0 to 100.

hh3cPUECVideoChannelID.name: hh3cPUECVideoChannelID
hh3cPUECVideoChannelID.description: The ID of the video channel

hh3cPUECVideoChannelName.name: hh3cPUECVideoChannelName
hh3cPUECVideoChannelName.description: The name of the video channel. It is suggested that the name includes the channel ID information.

hh3cPUECVideoChannelServiceStatus.name: hh3cPUECVideoChannelServiceStatus
hh3cPUECVideoChannelServiceStatus.description: The service status of the video channel. 0 the status is not known. 1 the video is not used or the channel has no signal. 2 the camera is kinescoping. 3 the camera is take snapshot.

hh3cPUDCRcvVideoPackets.name: hh3cPUDCRcvVideoPackets
hh3cPUDCRcvVideoPackets.description: The total number of video packets which are received from interfaces.

hh3cPUDCRcvVideoRefFrames.name: hh3cPUDCRcvVideoRefFrames
hh3cPUDCRcvVideoRefFrames.description: The total number of video reference frames which are received from interfaces.

hh3cPUDCVideoPacketsLoss.name: hh3cPUDCVideoPacketsLoss
hh3cPUDCVideoPacketsLoss.description: The total number of lost video packets.

hh3cPUDCVideoRefFramesLoss.name: hh3cPUDCVideoRefFramesLoss
hh3cPUDCVideoRefFramesLoss.description: The total number of lost video reference frames.

hh3cPUECManExternalSemaphoreTrap.name: hh3cPUECManExternalSemaphoreTrap
hh3cPUECManExternalSemaphoreTrap.description: Send a trap about external semaphore alarm.

hh3cPUECManVideoLossTrap.name: hh3cPUECManVideoLossTrap
hh3cPUECManVideoLossTrap.description: Send a trap about video loss. Video loss is that no video signal is inputted to the EC.

hh3cPUECManVideoRecoverTrap.name: hh3cPUECManVideoRecoverTrap
hh3cPUECManVideoRecoverTrap.description: Send a trap about video recovery after loss.

hh3cPUECManMotionDetectTrap.name: hh3cPUECManMotionDetectTrap
hh3cPUECManMotionDetectTrap.description: Send a trap about motion detection.

hh3cPUECManOnLineFailureTrap.name: hh3cPUECManOnLineFailureTrap
hh3cPUECManOnLineFailureTrap.description: Send a trap when EC can not register the CMS.

hh3cPUECManConnectionCMSFailureTrap.name: hh3cPUECManConnectionCMSFailureTrap
hh3cPUECManConnectionCMSFailureTrap.description: Send a trap when the connection with the CMS breaks down.

hh3cPUECManConnectionVerSrvFailureTrap.name: hh3cPUECManConnectionVerSrvFailureTrap
hh3cPUECManConnectionVerSrvFailureTrap.description: Send a trap when the connection with the version server breaks down or can not create.

hh3cPUECManFlashFailureTrap.name: hh3cPUECManFlashFailureTrap
hh3cPUECManFlashFailureTrap.description: Send a trap about flash failure.

hh3cPUECManCameraShelterTrap.name: hh3cPUECManCameraShelterTrap
hh3cPUECManCameraShelterTrap.description: Send a trap when a camera is sheltered.

hh3cPUECRegionCoordinateX1.name: hh3cPUECRegionCoordinateX1
hh3cPUECRegionCoordinateX1.description: The horizontal coordinate of top left point of the motion detection region.

hh3cPUECRegionCoordinateY1.name: hh3cPUECRegionCoordinateY1
hh3cPUECRegionCoordinateY1.description: The vertical coordinate of top left point of the motion detection region.

hh3cPUECRegionCoordinateX2.name: hh3cPUECRegionCoordinateX2
hh3cPUECRegionCoordinateX2.description: The horizontal coordinate of botton right point of the motion detection region.

hh3cPUECRegionCoordinateY2.name: hh3cPUECRegionCoordinateY2
hh3cPUECRegionCoordinateY2.description: The horizontal coordinate of botton right point of the motion detection region.
